OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774033868
OL,3,COfficer sprayed with shattered glass
OL,4,Cas car crashes into them at speed
OL,6,FA Met Police officer was left covered
OL,7,Fin shattered glass after a driver
OL,8,Freversed into her and a colleague
OL,9,Fwhile they tried to stop a suspected
OL,10,Fstolen car in Barnet.
OL,12,FPC Angel De Melo was in the passenger
OL,13,Fseat when their vehicle was struck on
OL,14,FSomerton Street. She described the
OL,15,Fmoment as terrifying.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
