PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774033868
OL,3,COfficer sprayed with shattered glass
OL,4,Cas car crashes into them at speed
OL,6,F"Everything happened so quickly, but
OL,7,Fin incidents like this, it feels like
OL,8,Ftime slows down," she said. "The wheel
OL,9,Fwas coming straight at my face. I
OL,10,Fbraced for it... then felt a mist of
OL,11,Fshattered glass all over me. In that
OL,12,Fmoment, I thought: this is it."
OL,14,FThe offending car, a Defender, mounted
OL,15,Fthe front of the police vehicle,
OL,16,Fcrushed the windscreen, rolled onto
OL,17,Fthe roof, and finally flipped onto its
OL,18,Fside.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]pD@]OUtD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774033868
OL,3,COfficer sprayed with shattered glass
OL,4,Cas car crashes into them at speed
OL,6,FDespite the terrifying crash, the
OL,7,Fofficers were not seriously injured.
OL,8,FThey pursued the driver after he ran
OL,9,Foff and arrested him a short time
OL,10,Flater.
OL,12,FPC Rishav Neupane, who was driving,
OL,13,Fsaid: "I've been rammed before, but
OL,14,Fnothing like this. I remember the
OL,15,Fsound of the windscreen crushing,
OL,16,Ftyres rolling over it, and the glass
OL,17,Fcollapsing. I honestly thought Angel
OL,18,Fwas going to be crushed."
OL,26,@uD@GOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
