OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774033868
OL,3,COfficer sprayed with shattered glass
OL,4,Cas car crashes into them at speed
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Christina Jessah,
OL,7,Fresponsible for policing in
OL,8,FWestminster and Kensington and
OL,9,FChelsea, praised the officers' bravery.
OL,11,F"The actions of these officers show
OL,12,Fpolicing at its very best: teamwork,
OL,13,Fresilience, and courage in the face of
OL,14,Fa real threat," she said. "Photographs
OL,15,Ffrom the scene show just how close
OL,16,Fthey were to serious, potentially life-
OL,17,Fchanging harm. We are incredibly
OL,18,Ffortunate they walked away ` and even
OL,19,Fmore so that they continued the
OL,20,Fpursuit and ensured the suspect's safe
OL,21,Farrest.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@OO]vD@[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
