OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774033868
OL,3,COfficer sprayed with shattered glass
OL,4,Cas car crashes into them at speed
OL,6,F"This incident highlights not only
OL,7,Ftheir individual courage but also the
OL,8,Fextraordinary heroism of frontline
OL,9,Fofficers across the Met every single
OL,10,Fday. Vehicles used as weapons pose
OL,11,Fenormous risks, yet our officers
OL,12,Fconfront these dangers with unwavering
OL,13,Fprofessionalism and determination."
